Concept:
========

Something like a game with primary the objective of implementing things I read on the internet, like A* pathfinding or behaviour trees AI. All this in Javascript.

Cloning instructions:
=====================

This project uses submodules, so you have to use the "--recursive" option:

git clone --recursive https://github.com/sgadrat/influence.git

Or you can do it in two steps :

git clone https://github.com/sgadrat/influence.git
cd influence/rtge
git submodule init
git submodule update

Browser compatibility:
======================

Chromium / Chrome: Works great
Firefox: Works
Microsoft Edge: Maybe (not tested)
Microsoft Internet Explorer: I don't think so (not tested)

